#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga "
msgstr "8. Perfection "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Sukhasomanassasutta "
msgstr "78. Joy and Happiness "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.431, sc1
msgctxt "an6.78:1.1"
msgid "“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu diṭṭheva dhamme sukhasomanassabahulo viharati, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a mendicant has six things they’re full of joy and happiness in the present life, and they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements. "

msgctxt "an6.78:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "an6.78:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dhammārāmo hoti, bhāvanārāmo hoti, pahānārāmo hoti, pavivekārāmo hoti, abyāpajjhārāmo hoti, nippapañcārāmo hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant enjoys the teaching, meditation, giving up, seclusion, kindness, and non-proliferation. "

msgctxt "an6.78:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu diṭṭheva dhamme sukhasomanassabahulo viharati, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāyā”ti. "
msgstr "When a mendicant has these six things they’re full of joy and happiness in the present life, and they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.78:1.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

